Short Desc:
Space Shooter game similar to Asteroids, Super R Type, Gradius, and Galaga.

Long Desc:
Serpentine is a Space Shooter game similar to popular arcade games like Asteroids, Super R Type, Gradius, and Galaga. You progress level to level by shooting down as many enemy craft as you can. You can submit and compare your High Scores with other players from all over the world. Control your ship by using the joystick on the bottom left and fire with the button on the bottom right.
I am always looking to make improvements and I value what my users send me so please let me know what you think through email or comments.

*disclaimer - I use a Push Ad in the Notification bar as a method to advertise and keep this app free. You can opt out from receiving the Ads at anytime from http://opt.leadbolt.com/

Tags: free arcade space shooter gamepad.
